Note: the entries on this page are outdated, please see the new PLT Technical Reports page.

PLT publishes technical reports about some of its tools and libraries so that scholars who wish to give proper credit to some of our innovations have a definite citation. Each entry below provides the full pdf and a bibtex entry; some of the bibtex entries provide additional citations to published papers.
